/smiles/tv/16.gif\" smileid=\"55\" alt=\"(bgm39)\"><br><br><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">为了放流买碟不如不买 (暴言)</span>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/30/183052.jpg","floor":"#10-1","id":"1514935","time":"2019-10-24 15:06","userId":"lee960707","userName":"hoshinokuzu","userSign":"","message":"非常感谢！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/56/205602.jpg","floor":"#10-2","id":"1514938","time":"2019-10-24 15:21","userId":"xiaowufeixia","userName":"逆淚","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">hoshinokuzu</span> 说: 非常感谢！</q></div>还有如果你买光驱是用来<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">播放</span>BD的话, 电脑上还要配PowerDVD之类的商业软件, 否则开源的播放器缺少密钥, 需要联网获取(这个表述不一定准确, 总之电脑上播一定会有一个解密的过程, 涉及多个密钥, 具体见AACS的加密原理)。当然如果你愿意折腾可以用VLC配合libaacs再去doom9、MakeMKV之类的论坛找密钥库手动加载也不是不可以。总之在电脑上想接上光驱就播很麻烦。推荐还是先抓出来放到本地后播放。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/61/36176.jpg","floor":"#10-3","id":"1516769","time":"2019-10-29 05:55","userId":"36176","userName":"豆沙包罐头","userSign":"","message":"<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">还是买了吧，RIP出来总比用光驱看来得强</span>"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/22/242277.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1514939","time":"2019-10-24 15:23","userId":"242277","userName":"DDpzj","userSign":"(要是种崎敦美或桑原由气宣布结婚我就声豚毕业 ... ...)","message":"mark，等预算宽裕一点打算入一个<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">或者直接买Playstation</span>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/16/11687.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1516713","time":"2019-10-28 23:48","userId":"11687","userName":"Emik","userSign":"","message":"光驱的话先锋建兴都可以，但电脑上播必须要买PowerDVD，如果想播UHD 4K那还必须要用Intel 7代以后的CPU（因为Intel SGX，AMD不支持）<br>不过动画没得4K，估计不存在这个问题，因此（不看4K的前提下）PS4其实是最简单的解决方案<br><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/30/183052.jpg","floor":"#12-1","id":"1516767","time":"2019-10-29 05:19","userId":"lee960707","userName":"hoshinokuzu","userSign":"","mes